et via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aSpeciesxPhilosophy. 4aHistory : History of Science. 7aSCIENCE / History.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9780791480885?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780791480885423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780791480885/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles